dcterms:description: The Sepsis Cases dataset records information about patients admitted to a Dutch hospital with symptoms of life-threatening sepsis. It includes events from patient registration in the emergency room to final discharge, with labels indicating whether the patient was admitted to intensive care.
dcterms:title: Sepsis Cases

dcterms:description: The BPIC2015 dataset consists of event logs from five Dutch municipalities, detailing their building permit application processes, with labels based on the satisfaction of specific LTL rules.
